column1: This file was created by CMPT_ME_BEME_RETS using the 201705 CRSP database.
It contains value- and equal-weighted returns for the intersections of  5
ME portfolios and  5 BE/ME portfolios.
The portfolios are constructed at the end of Jun.  ME is market cap at the end
of Jun.  BE/ME is book equity at the last fiscal year end of the prior calendar
year divided by ME as of  6 months before formation.  Firms with negative
BE are not included in any portfolio.
The annual returns are from January to December.
Missing data are indicated by -99.99 or -999.
The break points include utilities and include financials.
The  portfolios  include utilities and include financials.
